Bryant St.', 'The Bryant Gardens apartments are the perfect place for anyone to call home.', 'They are located in Englewood near Hampden and Federal.', 'Enjoy the ease of having RiverPoint Shopping Center, numerous dining options and a theater close by.', 'Slightly farther out you can find baseball fields, local parks, a recreation center, several local schools and Chuck E Cheese.', 'Stay comfortable and warm with a furnace and water heater in each unit, large bright rooms, and on site laundry for your convenience.', 'Come be a part of the Bryant Gardens Community and apply today!', 'Manager Chris', 'show contact info', '.', 'No pets please.', '**', "**We are looking for a tenant with previous rental history and verifiable income around 2.5x's the rent.", 'We also check credit and criminal history.', 'If there is an issue in any area you may be required to pay a larger deposit.', 'The application fee is $40 per adult.', '****', 'INCO Property Management & Sales', 'Leasing Department', '6640 S Broadway Suite A', 'Centennial, CO 80121', 'View Website: <URL>']
